commentTextItems.html: Plunkett to Kaneria, good line and length delivery, Kaneria drives it away past cover but the deep cover in to keep it to one, 1 run
Plunkett to Arshad Khan, good line but full, Arshad Khan drives the ball through the off side, deep point cuts it off, 1 run
Plunkett to Kaneria, length ball, Kaneria drives on the on side, not timed, runs away towards long-on who is in very quick, 1 run
Plunkett to Kaneria, down the leg side, Kaneria drives on the front foot straight at midwicket, no runs

Plunkett to Arshad Khan, good length delivery, Arshad Khan drives the ball through the off side, short cover can not hold on, run taken, throw is wide, they nearly run on the overthrow, decide not to, 1 run
Anderson to Arshad Khan, line and length, Arshad Khan slashes the drive to the deep cover sweeper, 1 run
